casebody.data:
Jessica SILVA, et al., Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
US BANK NATIONAL ASSOCIATION, etc., et al., Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D18-0764 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. SEPTEMBER 13, 2018 SUAREZ, LOGUE and LINDSEY, JJ., concur.

ORDERED that appellee US Bank National Association, as Trustee's motion to dismiss appeal is granted, and this appeal from the Circuit Court for Miami-Dade County, Florida is hereby dismissed.
